description: Presidential Secretariat - Notifying that Hon. Patalee Champika MP. resigned the office of Minister of Technology & Research w.e.f.18.11.2014. Notifying tht the President has removed Hon. Pallewatte gamaralalage Maitripala Sirisena, MP. Minister of Health, Hon. Rajitha Senaratne, MP. Minister of Fisheries & Acquatic Resources Development & Hon. Duminida Dissanayake MP, Minister of Education Services, from the office of Minister w.e.f. 21.11.2014. Notifying that the President has removed Hon. M.K.A.D.S.Gunawardana, MP, Deputy Minister of Buddha Sasana & Religious Affairs, from the office of Deputy Minister w.e.f. 21.11.2014
